  <CalDefinition Description="This Calibration controls the pop-up appearance time (delay) after interaction with certain settings. MY 21. Mid / High Radio. Global B " Name="UniqueSmallPopUp_Time_Delayed" References="GIS-552 5.1.1.1 MY21 Calibration Items" Usage="MID,HIGH,GLOBALB,VCU">
